Fair enough, but is the monk's orange headband quest to be changed? I'm about to start it and will hold off for a bit if it is. Come to think of it, if it isn't either. Running into Paw and finding it suddenly mid-level would be a rather nasty shock.<BR><BR>
</FONT>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ariel" COLOR="#FF0000">
